features: 🌻 SPIRAL NOTEBOOK - 3 pack A5 spiral notebooks contains 3 × 160 pages with rounded corner for easier carrying, back pocket to store your loose item, and the elastic closure band to keep your notebook close when you don’t use it. The size of this journal is 6" × 8.3", which is a perfect size for carrying!

🌻 RULED JOURNAL DESIGN - The ruled notebook is designed with oil painting patterns as its theme, and there are three different patterns available. Also, this journal adopts a sturdy twin-wire binding design, making it easy to lay the notebook completely flat and flip pages, providing a better writing experience.

🌻 PREMIUM THICK PAPER - In order to avoid the ink feathering and seepage, this ruled journal uses high quality and thick paper which is thicker than other journals. 7mm ruled writing space provide an ample place to jot down your notes, ideas, plans and so on.

🌻 FEATURES - The journal for women with an elastic closure, it makes the notebook/ journal close firmly, it can also be used as a bookmark stuck in the place where you wrote last time. And an inner pocket on the last page, you can place some small cards, business cards.

🌻 MULTIPLE USES - Ideal for all office, school and home uses, including for taking notes and keeping work in order, as a diary or journal for brainstorming ideas, creative writing or just doodling and drawing to your hearts content. Also, it is a perfect a gift choice for friends, family, classmates, and coworkers!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 6, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Sturdy, Perfect Size, Pretty
reviews.reviewText: The fact that you get 3 of these perfectly sized notebooks for this great price, should be enough to buy them! But aside from that bonus, the notebooks are sturdy (not flimsy) and they have a pocket and gold elastic marker band to mark your place when you're done. Each have a unique (but similar) artistic feature on their cover. They're big enough to write many manifestations or daily notes, but small enough to carry in your purse or portfolio.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 21, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Lovely and just the right size
reviews.reviewText: I love that the cover is not a real hardcover but also not soft. It's like sturdy cardboard and absolutely beautiful ! I want to give two as gifts but can't decide which one I want to keep; they are all so beautiful. I also like that it is spiral. This will be great for work or just for taking notes if you want something smaller than 8x11. If these don't go up on price I'll be getting more.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 22, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Very pretty and good quality
reviews.reviewText: I purchased these as gifts for co-workers. I was pleasantly surprised at how nice they are. The cover is sturdy (heavy cardboard not plastic but still sturdy), the pages are thick (not see through). Since they are gifts I haven't tested writing in them but judging by the thickness of the pages I do not think ink will bleed through. I like the gold elastic bookmark and there is a little pocket in the back cover as well. Overall, I am very happy with them and will purchase again as gifts or even for myself.

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Very Nice Notebooks/Journals
reviews.reviewText: These notebooks/journals are very sturdy, easy to use due to the lay-flat design with the spiral binding, and nice that there is an elastic closure for them. Very pretty and a great value for the price

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 26, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Better than expected
reviews.reviewText: Arrived on time and in condition as it should. Looks better and more sturdy in person than expected. Will be divided and given as part of a gift. Cost per notebook is okay as they look nicer than school supplies, but would not pay that much if just for my own use.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 27, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars PRETTY AND PRACTICAL
reviews.reviewText: These notebooks are so pretty! There was a pack of 3 but I gifted one to my Granddaughter. The colors are mid tone pastel florals. They are sturdy cardboard type paper jacket and the pages are lined and also has the top right of each page the No. and Date. I plan to use one of these beauties as my 2024 "bill book" to list bills & payment amounts & dates. I added vertical lines to form columns for the amount paid & the date paid. My Grandaughter uses her book for computer passwords. I recommend these pretty & useful books.
